query:
SELECT 
                spl_mint_token_address,
                address,
                amount,
                frequency,
                member_address_list,
                destination_address_list,
                multi_sig_account_address,
                vault_index,
                created_at,
                config_account_address FROM spendinglimit
            WHERE
                multi_sig_account_address = $1
                AND cardinality(member_address_list) = 1
                AND cardinality(destination_address_list) = 1
                AND member_address_list[1] = $2
                AND destination_address_list[1] = $3
            ORDER BY created_at ASC
